Name: Install Files
Description:
Before You Install 
We recommend that you use a separate, non-production machine for installing the reference pack or create a backup image of your computer, before installing any of the software referenced here. Alternatively, use a Virtual PC. This application has been tested on Windows 2003 Server SP2.

Following are the software requirements for the target machine:
1.	Windows Server 2003 Enterprise Edition
2.	Internet Information Services 6.0
3.	Microsoft .NET Framework 3.0
4.	Microsoft Office SharePoint Server 2007
5.	Microsoft Office 2007 Client Install (Word 2007, Excel 2007, Outlook 2007)
6.	OpenXMLSDK
How to Install 
In order to install the package follow these steps:
1)	Double-click the file OLBSetup.msi.
2)	Enter the required details as to Site URL in the screens that follow
a.	Site URL
b.	User Id
c.	Email address
3)	Wait for the console programs to finish execution
4)	Access the URL http://<ComputerName>:<portno>
Manual Configurations
No manual configuration
